org.spongepowered.api.entity.living

Interface Agent

  • All Superinterfaces:
    DataHolder, Entity, EntityState, Identifiable, Living
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    Aerial, Ageable, Ambient, Animal, Aquatic, Bat, Blaze, Boss, CaveSpider, Chicken, Cow, Creeper, EnderDragon, Enderman, Endermite, Ghast, Giant, Golem, Guardian, Horse, IronGolem, MagmaCube, Monster, Mooshroom, Ocelot, Pig, Rabbit, Sheep, Silverfish, Sittable, Skeleton, Slime, SnowGolem, Spider, Squid, Tameable, Villager, Witch, Wither, Wolf, Zombie, ZombiePigman

    public interface Agent
extends Living
    An Agent represents a Living that has AI. In the future Sponge will allow for custom AIs, but for now vanilla behavior can only be disabled.
